latestIgtvVideos.title: Glow routine with @rasluxuryoils ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I never really followed a skin care routine, but over the course of the lockdown, I’ve been trying to stick to a pretty simple one :) 

•Start by prepping your face with the Ras Rose Nectar face & body spritz. This toner works as a natural astringent, and leaves your skin feeling refreshed and nourished!

•Next, I’ve used the Ras Radiance beauty boosting elixir. This oil is lightweight, and gives the skin an instant glow ✨ 

Pro tip: can be used as a primer before you apply your foundation as well! 

•And finally, I move on to the Jade facial roller. The Jade facial roller is known to 
1) improve blood circulation 
2) reduce facial puffiness 
3) allow for better absorption of skin care products 
So if you want to get your glow on, I highly recommend these products 👌🏻

Managed by @yzarinay
